        walkthrough = 'First head to a Conquest Overseer either in your home city or Jeuno. Trade them enough Crystals (4+), until your Rank bar is almost or completely full.\n1. To flag the Mission, speak with Nelcabrit, then click the Door: San d\'Orian Emb. in Ru\'Lude Gardens (G-10) for the [Key Item] Archducal audience permit.\n   - The 3rd door on the left in the San d\'Orian Embassy is the correct one.\n2. Click on the Door: Audience Chamber in Ru\'Lude Gardens (H-5) for a cutscene and the [Key Item] Letter to Aldo.\n3. Speak to Aldo in Lower Jeuno, in the back of the Neptune\'s Spire Tenshodo H.Q. for a cutscene and the [Key Item] Silver bell.\n   - If you have done this mission in a other Nation then you already have the bell, but you still need to talk to him for a cutscene.\n4. Obtain the 3 Magicite Key Items. See below for details.\n5. Click the Audience Chamber in Ru\'Lude Gardens (H-5) after obtaining all 3 Magicites for a cutscene and your reward (either an [Key Item] Airship Pass, or, if you already have one, 20,000 Gil).\n6. Return to Nelcabrit in the San d\'Orian Embassy to complete the mission, receive 10,000 Gil and [Key Item] Message to Jeuno (San d\'Oria).',
